Write a simple java program for print following a star pattern.

*
**
***
****

Here's a simple Java program that prints the star pattern you requested

public class StarPattern {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        for (int i = 1; i <= 4; i++) {
            for (int j = 1; j <= i; j++) {
                System.out.print("*");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
